            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0016</span>
            <a href="http://www.mscui.net/DesignGuide/QuickGuides/DateTimeInput/Date/CalInput/instructions.aspx">Provide access to relevant instructional text (for example, via tooltips) on the clickable elements in the calendar header</a>
