        <div class="cui-rule error">
            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0018</span>
            <a href="http://www.mscui.net/DesignGuide/QuickGuides/DateTimeInput/Date/CalInput/keyboard.aspx">Display the appropriate value in the free text field following selection of the date</a>
            <span class="highlight">Mandatory</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cui-rule error">
            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0019</span>
