            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0011</span>
            <a href="http://www.mscui.net/DesignGuide/QuickGuides/DateTimeInput/Date/CalInput/editing.aspx">Provide the ability to select a month independently, and a year independently. Signify the interactivity of these elements by suitable styling, for example as buttons or links, and ensure that they have descriptive tooltips</a>
