    <div class="column-half">
        <div class="cui-rule warning">
            <span class="cui-ref">D+Tc-0008</span>
            <a href="http://www.mscui.net/DesignGuide/QuickGuides/DateTimeInput/Date/freetext.aspx">Allow the input of 'Unknown' (or similar) to specify dates not known to the user</a>
